Dear customer service team,
Recently I had ordered a product and upon opening the package, it was found
in a damaged state. Can u please help me with the return or replacement
process.
Thank you

Dear [Customer Service],
   I received a different item than what I ordered. My order
#1268390025368392 should have contained dyson airwrap, but I received
philips hair dryer. Can you assist me with returning the incorrect item and
sending the right one?
   Regards,
   Katyaini
